{"tid":1826424,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：駱惠寧認親認戚扮一家人 - 李八方","createTime":"2020-01-16T06:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T07:17:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"df8638feb3df1a824adf8184ec37a52fa16f6696","tid":1826424,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T06:27:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200116/5PWV7LFZUQ4RLYPWI7RURF5GZA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200116%2F5PWV7LFZUQ4RLYPWI7RURF5GZA%2F&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GKhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=d816495f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200116%2F5PWV7LFZUQ4RLYPWI7RURF5GZA%2F&h=5a33237f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200116/5PWV7LFZUQ4RLYPWI7RURF5GZA/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：駱惠寧認親認戚扮一家人 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200116/large/1579105418_42a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200116%2Flarge%2F1579105418_42a6.jpg&h=b3c77b10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n駱惠寧嚟咗香港做中聯辦主任，噚日就要主持中聯辦新春酒會，致辭嗰陣又係大讚特首林鄭月娥帶領管治團隊同警隊止暴制亂，表現出非常時期嘅非常勇氣，已經唔使對佢有乜幻想，不過佢似乎想扮吓好人，不斷講乜嘢一家人之間有商有量，唔使用暴力，可惜網民唔多受落，紛紛話冇人想同打到人頭破血流嘅人做一家人！<br />\n<br />\n抄習總講「家和萬事興」<br />\n<br />\n駱惠寧喺致辭話，香港係多元社會，對一啲問題存在不同意見，甚至有重大分歧並唔奇怪，但不能走極端更不能搞暴力，強調一家人之間有商有量，再大嘅事都可解決，佢又提及習近平視察澳門時講「家和萬事興」，仲話自己作為香港呢個家嘅一員，已感受到家人嘅親切，又引用《獅子山下》歌詞「拋開區分求共對」，叫人攜手為香港呢個家打拼奮鬥。<br />\n<br />\n不過好多網民話冇人想同佢做一家人，仲話𠵱家呢個家有家暴，日日俾777同班green objects欺凌，仲打到人頭破血流、見人就又拉又鎖，冇人想同佢哋做家人，駱惠寧仲大讚呢班人，點會有香港人認同！"},{"pid":"5f6660e14a494e11168d45831c2eea58fe418522","tid":1826424,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T06:29:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">腳震仔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"9812d35002822b1d6b48d035ecdaf0d48e483e0c","tid":1826424,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T06:36:21.000Z","msg":"嘥氣，點扮都知你唔係一家人"},{"pid":"e8e473be71ca53aa446a009357b68b379a434e76","tid":1826424,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T07:17:35.000Z","msg":"天啟四騎士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}